The Pantheon Equation

I think every Pantheon artifact is trying to satisfy something like:

Meaning = Structure × Context × Execution

Remove structure:

You get disconnected facts.

Remove context:

You get brittle abstractions.

Remove execution:

You get elegant but inert ideas.

All three interact.

